      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KRUMAC (4) missed a whisker here and then missed by just 1L over 1400m in stronger at Eagle Farm. That's good form, and he hits this at peak. Well placed to post his second win. WANTED HILLBILLY (1) resumed over 1100m at Ipswich, beaten 2 lengths after being in contention on the corner. He will skip over and post handy. Drops back a level and should be in the finish. MISTER MIGHTY (2) surprised the market winning his Maiden first up this track/trip. Has the inside barrier and has plenty of scope for improvement. ELRONTE (8) resumed with a 1.3L defeat at Ipswich and then was plainer in a CL2 at Grafton, off a wide gate. Draws inside today and is still shy of her best. Has to be considered. CITY OF TEARS (3) gets in well with the 2kg claim back in grade and is showing promise.",
